I wanted to take a minute to reflect on the terrible tragedy that happened Sunday amidst the celebration. I was unable to post these wonderful pictures from Grammy night, as our family has been grieving this sudden loss of Kobe Bryant, with whom my husband went to school with.  Our hearts are with all the families whose lives were lost. Life is a circle and with light is dark, so I'm celebrating the light today and the highlights from The Grammys @recordingacademy because it deserves to be celebrated! Congratulations to my friend, @robkinelski who won his first Grammys with @billieeilish  I'm looking forward to more!
Getting excited for The Grammy Awards TONIGHT on @cbstv 5pm PST / 8PM EST
